1
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,520
What did you see in the cellar?

2
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:11,450
Don't look at me.

3
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:12,890
Don't look at me.

4
00:01:14,360 --> 00:01:15,289
Don't look at me.

5
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:16,570
Don't look at me.

6
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,980
Don't look at me. Don't look at me.

7
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:24,960
It seems he was severely traumatized.

8
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:27,289
We won't be able to get anything out of him.

9
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,000
Hey, Zhai.

10
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:35,640
Speak.

11
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:36,759
Master.

12
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:39,400
We also found traces of a woman in the cellar,

13
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:41,000
and they were left recently.

14
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,360
Yang Xiaomei.

15
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:45,440
Over the past few days,

16
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:47,240
