17
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:48,080
Locked up.

18
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:49,440
Think carefully.

19
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:52,039
We are the police.

20
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,600
Don't be afraid.

21
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,600
We will help you catch all

22
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:57,020
those who bullied you.

23
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,840
I'll be obedient.

24
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,080
That's not what I meant.

25
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:01,760
Think about whether there are other women.

26
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:02,160
You.

27
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,560
Hey.

28
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,650
Pig... Pig-killing knife.

29
