Chop him.

30
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,740
What kind of knife?

31
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:15,160
Pi... Pig-killing knife.

32
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,480
A pig-killing knife.

33
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:18,560
A butcher.

34
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,000
Xiao Zhai.

35
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,760
Wang Xichuan has an accomplice.

36
00:02:22,760 --> 00:02:23,800
He's most likely a butcher.

37
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,860
Look into it for me.

38
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:27,400
One of Wang Xichuan's cousins is a butcher

39
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,400
named Yang Zhigang.

40
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,480
I took Yang Zhigang from the slaughterhouse last night.

41
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:31,610
Send me his address.

42
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:40,200
Hehe.

43
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,130
So sweet.

44
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:50,380
That's too good for Wang Xichuan and his son.

45
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:51,800
But,

46
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,560
I'm going to have some fun today too.

47
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,600
Hehe.

48
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:57,200
Hehe.

49
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:57,720
Ouch.

50
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,440
Who is it?

51
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,000
Don't move.

52
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,840
Who is it?

53
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,320
Get up.

54
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,120
Officer.

55
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,280
I'm innocent!

56
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,000
I...

57
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:08,320
I just smelled it.

58
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:09,200
I didn't do anything.

59
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:09,720
A misunderstanding, right?

60
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:10,050
Move.

61
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,120
Let's find another place for this misunderstanding.

62
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:11,840
I'm innocent!

63
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,960
Oh, officer.

64
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,840
Don't be afraid.

65
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,840
We are the police.

66
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,340
We are taking you to the hospital now.

67
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,530
The day I stayed in Wangwu Village,

68
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,800
I just happened to pass by that slaughterhouse.

69
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,800
If only I had gone in and taken a look,

70
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,329
maybe Lin Xiaoai

71
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:38,200
could have been rescued earlier.

72
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:38,720
Sigh.

73
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,860
Don't be too hard on yourself.

74
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:43,520
You were so busy asking so many villagers that day.

75
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,850
How could you have known

76
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,400
Butcher Yang was involved?

77
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,800
That Butcher Yang

78
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,320
looked pretty normal.

79
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,520
I'm just too inexperienced.

80
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,640
If it were my master,

81
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,440
he definitely would have noticed something wrong.

82
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:54,920
Oh.

83
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:55,800
Captain Gu.

84
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,280
Ah.

85
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,220
Notice what wrong?

86
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:00,140
Captain Gu.

87
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,160
Master.

88
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:04,460
Did you find Wang Xichuan's head?

89
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,600
Do I look like I found it?

90
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,800
We searched the slaughterhouse and Butcher Yang's home inside out,

91
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:09,860
but found nothing.

92
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:11,680
Hey, Master.

93
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,720
You haven't eaten yet, have you?

94
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:16,440
This is all that's left in the cafeteria.

95
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:18,200
Or I can go buy you a boxed lunch.

96
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:18,860
No need.

97
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,000
This is fine.

98
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:21,600
Gu.

99
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:23,320
Do you want the instant noodles I have here?

100
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,400
No need. Give it to Qiu Chen.

101
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,800
Qiu Chen hasn't eaten either, right?

102
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,360
Thanks.

103
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,560
I don't eat junk food.

104
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,480
You only eat candy every day.

105
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,360
Are you trying to become an immortal?

106
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,159
Give it to me if you don't want it.

107
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,280
I'll make it for you.

108
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:36,140
Suit yourself.

109
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:38,440
Oops.

110
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:43,120
Oh, right.

111
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,060
Captain Gu.

112
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,920
The Investigation Department sent a document this morning.

113
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,320
It says that the substance extracted

114
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:50,200
from the bones in the sorghum field

115
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:52,920
is highly consistent with the samples extracted from the cellar.

116
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:54,320
We can basically confirm

117
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:57,659
that they were trapped in that cellar before they died.

118
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,320
Scumbag.

119
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,080
Master.

120
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:04,960
I'm not eating.

121
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,560
Investigate Wang Mingming.

122
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,140
-Hey, hey, hey.

123
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:10,090
I'll go interrogate Butcher Yang.

124
00:05:10,280 --> 00:05:12,340
Have a bite before you go, Captain Gu.

125
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:14,960
Wang Xichuan.

126
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,540
Wang Mingming,

127
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,320
how do you explain this?

128
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,400
Explain what?

129
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,600
If I say

130
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,240
my dad did this,

131
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:31,800
I know nothing about it,

132
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,040
and it has nothing to do with me,

133
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,240
would you believe me?

134
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,400
We found traces of you

135
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,720
living in there long-term.

136
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,450
How dare you say you don't know?

137
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,240
Also,

138
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:50,440
the two female bodies in the crop field,

139
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,300
what's going on with them?

140
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:57,700
Wang Mingming,

141
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,240
don't think

142
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:01,480
you can push everything onto a dead man.

143
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,000
Yeah.

144
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,200
Confess.

145
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:11,440
After my mom died when I was young,

146
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:14,010
that cellar was already there.

147
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,160
I wanted to go out and play,

148
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,420
but he wouldn't let me.

149
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:24,040
He insisted I watch him screw women.

150
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,080
When I grew up,

151
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,800
he brought me along.

152
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,520
Being stuck with a dad like that,

153
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,400
what could I do?

154
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,380
[Sighs]

155
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:36,159
Your dads are probably pretty good, right?

156
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,340
Look how well they raised you,

157
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,130
becoming police officers.

158
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,930
I didn't ask you about this.

159
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,640
Talk about your own problem.

160
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:44,640
Ah.

161
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,440
My dad said

162
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,640
those city girls

163
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,240
are strangers here,

164
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:53,880
easiest to trick.

165
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:57,159
Under the guise of fortune-telling, we'd lure them home,

166
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,800
and then secretly

167
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,920
drug the talisman water they drank.

168
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,600
Then...

169
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:11,120
Then...

170
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,560
[Sobbing]

171
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,680
Get up.

172
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,450
[Chuckling]

173
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,520
[Laughing]

174
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:40,640
Those girls were tortured to death by you two,

175
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:43,240
and then dragged to the crop field to be buried.

176
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:45,370
The so-called haunted crop field,

177
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,400
right?

178
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,440
Ah!

179
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:55,600
The person was already dead.

180
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,360
Why did he have to cut off her head,

181
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,420
put it in a wine jar,

182
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,240
and throw it into the cellar?

183
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,000
My dad said

184
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:04,720
if her head was cut off,

185
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,760
even if the police found the body,

186
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:08,880
they wouldn't be able to identify her.

187
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,000
Also,

188
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:12,160
it could scare the newly arrived girls

189
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,490
and make them obedient.

190
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,320
And...

191
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,160
And what?

192
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,480
Also, he said

193
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,200
letting the dead woman

194
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:30,000
watch him sleep with new women

195
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,330
made it more thrilling.

196
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:36,039
What a psycho.

197
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:38,620
Come on,

198
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,010
tell me about Yang Xiaomei.

199
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,640
Yang Xiao...

200
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:47,360
Ah,

201
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,720
her.

202
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,400
Uh...

203
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,040
[Coughs]

204
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:56,000
My dad said our horoscopes matched,

205
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,700
and he wanted her to be my wife.

206
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,240
Craving alcohol again?

207
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:05,840
Yeah.

208
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,640
Officer.

209
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,280
Could it really be

210
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,520
that the dead women

211
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:16,560
turned into ghosts and killed my father?

212
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:18,820
Ghosts don't use butcher knives to kill.

213
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:21,570
You must know Yang Zhigang, right?

214
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:29,400
I mean, how did you find out about him?

215
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:30,740
This...

216
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,440
Right.

217
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:32,900
I remember now.

218
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,720
He must be the one who killed my father!

219
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:36,000
Investigate him!

220
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,640
What's his relationship with you two?

221
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,840
Are you accomplices?

222
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:41,880
That stupid idiot...

223
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:43,600
Watch your mouth.

224
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,080
He is...

225
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:48,120
my father's distant relative,

226
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:48,800
my uncle.

227
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,800
We gave the women we killed

228
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:51,860
to him to deal with.

229
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,680
He chopped off their heads,

230
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:56,010
and we buried the bodies in the cornfield.

231
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:57,900
Then we'd pay him for his trouble.

232
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:03,560
We didn't interact much.

233
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:04,440
Ah.

234
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:06,920
Idiot.

235
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,240
A while ago, he didn't have money,

236
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,640
so he came to borrow some.

237
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,600
Then,

238
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,720
my father refused to give him any.

239
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:16,360
He cursed and threatened to tell everyone about the cellar,

240
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,560
to let everyone know.

241
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:19,160
Then...

242
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,880
Then the two of them started fighting,

243
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,000
and got physical.

244
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:24,480
Sigh.

245
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:26,400
Officer,

246
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:29,530
I've told you everything I should.

247
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:31,560
I feel like

248
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:33,620
my life has been pretty meaningless.

249
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,320
That old bastard

250
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,720
raised me to be like this.

251
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:39,760
Just shoot me.

252
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:44,600
Whether you get shot or not

253
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,640
isn't up to you.

254
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,170
It's decided by the law.

255
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:50,240
Officer,

256
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:52,040
I'm really innocent!

257
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:54,960
Officer!

258
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,640
Look at these photos.

259
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:01,920
Oh.

260
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,240
I really don't know them.

261
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,840
I haven't seen these photos.

262
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,680
Dare you say

263
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:10,520
you know nothing about Wang Xichuan and his son's dealings?

264
00:11:10,520 --> 00:11:12,880
The heads of the two corpses in Qingshazhang,

265
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,480
you cut them off, didn't you?

266
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:18,320
Yes.

267
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:20,320
I... I did indeed

268
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,920
help... help them

269
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,920
dispose of two corpses.

270
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:26,400
But that was a long time ago.

271
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,840
Wang Xichuan is really shrewd.

272
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:31,260
He only gave me a little money.

273
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,000
But,

274
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,980
I didn't fall out with him either.

275
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,730
A couple of days ago,

276
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:39,050
I went to borrow money from him.

277
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:49,480
Wang Xichuan.

278
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:55,210
Who is it?

279
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:56,760
Stop knocking!

280
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:57,560
Open the door now.

281
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:58,620
In broad daylight.

282
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:00,720
Zhigang.

283
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,000
Locking the door in broad daylight,

284
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:04,240
what kind of dirty deeds are you doing inside?

285
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,000
Zhigang.

286
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:07,780
It's not that I don't want to help you.

287
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,420
I don't have money either.

288
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,920
All my money

289
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:13,090
went to that little bastard

290
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:15,160
for drinking and gambling.

291
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:17,000
Don't try to fool me.

292
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:19,160
My money is all hard-earned.

293
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,920
Unlike you father and son,

294
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:22,080
who just move your lips

295
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,200
and scam money.

296
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:24,820
You swindle and cheat.

297
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:27,820
Say whatever you want.

298
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,320
I really don't

299
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:30,880
have money now.

300
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:31,760
Go

301
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,360
find other relatives.

302
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:35,080
You,

303
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,740
Stop putting on an act with me.

304
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:37,570
Careful,

305
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:40,290
or I'll expose the dirty deeds in your cellar.

306
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:43,560
Those things,

307
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:45,780
you were involved too.

308
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,880
Exposing it

309
00:12:48,800 --> 00:12:49,660
won't do anyone

310
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:51,800
any good.

311
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:53,160
Oh, come on.

312
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,600
Still talking about doing no good.

313
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:58,600
Those women were all tricked by you father and son.

314
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:00,600
I only got my turn after you were done.

315
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,120
I'm an accomplice at most.

316
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:04,040
I'll do a couple of years and get out.

317
00:13:04,040 --> 00:13:04,520
But you,

318
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:06,280
you'll die in there, you know?

319
00:13:06,280 --> 00:13:08,240
You acting mysterious every day,

320
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,600
doing this crap.

321
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,730
This won't save you.

322
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:13,180
Playing the devil won't save you either.

323
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:14,720
Give me the money.

324
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,160
Look.

325
00:13:22,160 --> 00:13:23,420
On the day of the crime,

326
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:25,600
what did you go to the Wangs' for?

327
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,400
I didn't go to the Wangs'.

328
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:28,840
That day,

329
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,520
I went to sleep early.

330
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:33,040
The next morning,

331
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,240
when I woke up,

332
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:37,640
I saw Wang Xichuan sent me a message in the middle of the night.

333
00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:38,680
He said

334
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:39,920
borrowing money

335
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:41,040
is negotiable,

336
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:42,000
ah,

337
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:44,520
and told me not to talk about his deeds.

338
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:47,120
He even said he'd give me a woman.

339
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:49,360
It's in my phone.

340
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:52,280
Look at the history if you don't believe me.

341
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:52,920
And then?

342
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:54,840
Then I thought,

343
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:56,480
what if it's true?

344
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:58,360
So I

345
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,920
planned to go and see.

346
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:00,980
But halfway there,

347
00:14:01,160 --> 00:14:02,620
I actually saw that woman.

348
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,160
From the looks of her,

349
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:06,440
you could tell she had escaped from

350
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,900
the Wang family's cellar.

351
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:14,490
I went to Wangwu Village

352
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:16,780
to have Wang Xichuan tell my fortune.

353
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:19,490
But he took me into the sorghum fields,

354
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:22,320
saying he'd do some luck-changing ritual.

355
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:25,890
Once we got there, he started getting handsy with me.

356
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:28,760
I felt something was wrong and tried to run.

357
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:31,920
He chased me, knocked me out, and took me to the cellar.

358
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:35,040
So you were there on the night of the murder.

359
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,680
What happened that night?

360
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:45,520
Did you hear any noises upstairs,

361
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:47,220
or anyone talking?

362
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:50,320
I was in the cellar that night.

363
00:14:51,040 --> 00:14:53,370
I vaguely heard people arguing upstairs.

364
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,840
But I was forced to drink the talisman water,

365
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,240
and quickly fell asleep.

366
00:14:58,400 --> 00:14:59,860
When I woke up the next day,

367
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:02,780
that crazy woman said Wang Xichuan was dead.

368
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,200
He's finally dead.

369
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:07,240
He's dead.

370
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:09,680
Hahaha.

371
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,560
I didn't believe it at first.

372
00:15:22,160 --> 00:15:23,360
But when I ran out to look,

373
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:24,690
there was really no one,

374
00:15:24,800 --> 00:15:25,680
so I escaped.

375
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:31,620
Lin Xiaoai, come take your medicine.

376
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:43,060
Now all four of them are suspected of murder.

377
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:45,160
Who exactly is lying?

378
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:48,210
Hey, Captain Gu,

379
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:50,160
Yang Zhigang's butcher knife

380
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:51,880
also has Wang Xichuan's blood on it.

381
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:53,940
Yang Zhigang has both the capability

382
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:55,500
and the motive to kill.

383
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:56,560
Right now,

384
00:15:56,560 --> 00:15:58,890
he is more suspicious than Wang Mingming.

385
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:00,130
Yang Zhigang

386
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:02,690
received Wang Xichuan's text at 3:00 a.m.

387
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:05,180
Wang Xichuan was already killed by then.

388
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:07,800
The text was definitely sent by the killer.

389
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:10,480
Could it be that Wang Mingming committed the murder,

390
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:11,480
and then

391
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:13,320
asked Yang Zhigang to help dismember the body?

392
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:13,800
Yes.

393
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:17,240
They have always coveted Wang Xichuan's property.

394
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:18,500
That's a possibility.

395
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:19,440
Yeah.

396
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:22,200
Qiu Chen,

397
00:16:22,880 --> 00:16:24,140
tell us what you think.

398
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:28,920
The word 'Sisters' on the cellar wall

399
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:31,760
should be a very important clue.

400
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:34,080
Ah, you mean

401
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,880
the murderer

402
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:37,600
is trying to stand up for the female victim in the cellar

403
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:38,600
and take revenge?

404
00:16:41,160 --> 00:16:43,480
The suspects Wang Mingming and Yang Zhigang

405
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:44,810
are both perpetrators.

406
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:47,810
Yang Xiaomei and Lin Xiaoai are both victims.

407
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,600
And Yang Xiaomei is crazy.

408
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,600
Is Yang Xiaomei

409
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,650
capable of taking revenge?

410
00:16:59,040 --> 00:17:00,040
Is Yang Xiaomei

411
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:01,680
really crazy?

412
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:12,119
A truly crazy person wouldn't care

413
00:17:12,119 --> 00:17:14,319
if they were exposed.

414
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:16,920
That's a sense of shame only a normal person has.

415
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:17,960
You suspect

416
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:20,930
she's faking it?

417
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:24,160
But even if she's sane,

418
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:26,599
she's been chained up for so long.

419
00:17:26,599 --> 00:17:28,329
Her muscles must be atrophied.

420
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:31,200
Is she still capable of killing and dismembering?

421
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:33,080
Just because she was chained up

422
00:17:33,280 --> 00:17:34,210
when we found her

423
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:36,440
doesn't mean she's always been.

424
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:41,800
I've observed the scars on her hands and feet,

425
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:43,130
and they're mostly old.

426
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:45,080
Besides,

427
00:17:45,520 --> 00:17:48,580
I've contacted the hospital to run a muscle test on her.

428
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:50,170
It's been confirmed

429
00:17:50,560 --> 00:17:52,820
that she currently has normal mobility.

430
00:17:58,840 --> 00:17:59,520
Contact

431
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:00,720
Yang Xiaomei's hometown immediately.

432
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,200
Have her assist with the investigation.

433
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,640
Arrange a psychiatric evaluation for her as soon as possible.

434
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:04,840
And a polygraph test.

435
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:05,280
Yes.

436
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,050
Stop eating.

437
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:09,600
Yes.

438
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:22,680
Under the bridge in front of the house,

439
00:18:23,560 --> 00:18:26,040
a flock of ducks swims by.
